# ── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Intentionally NOT ignored (committed by design):
#   - project-docs/.meta/**  (AIT version metadata, changes, snapshots — audit trail)
#   - project-docs/versions/** (AIT version workspaces)
#   - project-docs/.meta/blocks-index*.yaml + links-index.yaml
#     (technically regeneratable via `ait reindex`, but committing avoids the
#      bootstrap step after clone and provides diff visibility)



